<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="fill">
	<head>
		<title>Rotator</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" 
      		  href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" 
      	   	  integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" 
			  crossorigin="anonymous">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" 
			  href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/help.css">
	</head>
	<body class="fill">
		<div class="container fill">
			<div class="max-width row top-bar">
				<div class="left-top-bar-half">
					<a href="/">
						<i class="align-left fa fa-chevron-left mini"
						   aria-hidden="true"></i>
					</a>
				</div>
				<div class="right-top-bar-half">
					<% if ( currentUser ) { %>
						<div class="text-container">
							<label id="loggedInText">
								<%= currentUser.username %>
							</label>
						</div>
						<a href="/user/logout">
							<i id="loggedUserIcon" class="green fa fa-user-circle-o mini" aria-hidden="true"></i>
						</a>
					<% } else { %>
						<a href="/user">
							<i class="fa fa-user-circle-o mini" aria-hidden="true"></i>
						</a>
					<% } %>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="main row">
				<h2 class="top">How to Play</h2>
				<hr class="top">
				<p class="explanation">
					Rotator is a puzzle game involving a grid of squares. In order to win, you
					 must rotate all the squares to the same color. There are two colors, and
					 rotating a square changes it to the other color. You can rotate a square by
					 clicking on it, but its neighbors will also rotate. Whenever you click a
					 square, the squares immediately above, below, to the left of, and to the
					 right of the clicked square will rotate as well. Let's look at a board with
					 16 squares in it and label each of them with a number:
				</p>
				<div class="max-width square-container">
					<div class="square-row">
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">1</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">2</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">3</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">4</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="square-row">
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">5</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">6</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">7</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">8</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="square-row">
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">9</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">10</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">11</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">12</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
					</div>
					<div class="square-row">
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">13</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">14</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">15</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
						<span class="fa-stack">
							<div class="fa-stack-2x help-square"></div>
							<div class="fa-stack-1x strong-container">
								<strong class="strong-label">16</strong>
							</div>
						</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p class="explanation">
					If you clicked on Square #6, then Square #2, Square #5, Square #6, Square #7,
					 and Square #10 would all rotate and switch color. Furthermore, if you clicked
					 on Square #13, only Square #9, Square #13, and Square #14 will rotate and
					 switch color. In other words, the square you click on will always be rotated
					 and any square directly above, below, to the left, or to the right will also
					 be rotated if it exists.
				</p>

				<h2 class="middle">Icons</h2>
				<hr class="middle">
				<div class="icon-description-container max-width">
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>New Game</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-plus-circle"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it creates a new randomly generated board of squares to
							 play on. Additionally, it will set the moves and time counters to
							 zero.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Reset</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-refresh"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it returns the board to the beginning before you rotated
							 any squares. If you clicked the new game icon, it will reset to the
							 newly created board. This will set the moves and time counters to
							 zero.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="icon-description-container max-width">
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Moves</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-repeat"></i>
						<p class="description">
							The number to the right of this icon represents the amount of moves
							 you have made in the current game.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Time</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i>
						<p class="description">
							The numbers to the right of this icon represent the amount of time you
							 have spent on the current game in the format of hours, minutes, and
							 seconds.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="icon-description-container max-width">
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Home</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-home"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it takes you to the home page.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Back</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-chevron-left"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it takes you to the previous page.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="icon-description-container max-width">
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>User</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-user-circle-o"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it takes you to the log in/sign up page.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Logout</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-user-circle-o green"></i>
						<p class="description">
							When clicked, it logs you out of your current account. This icon only
							 appears when you are logged in.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="icon-description-container last max-width">
					<div class="icon-description">
						<strong>Victory Star</strong>
						<i class="fa fa-star green"></i>
						<p class="description">
							This icon appears when you win the game. If you click the reset or the
							 new game icon, this icon will disappear as the new game starts.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>